#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:9
msgid "Sphinxドキュメントのビルド性能を改善する"
msgstr "Improving build performance of Sphinx documentation"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:11
msgid ""
"Sphinxを使った多言語ドキュメントの構築において、ビルド時間が長くなってきたことをきっかけに、性能改善を行いました。この記事では、改善前後の状況や、試行錯誤のプロセス、そして得られた成果を整理しておきます。"
msgstr ""
"When building multilingual documents using Sphinx, we made performance "
"improvements as the build time became longer. In this article, I will "
"summarize the situation before and after the improvement, the process of "
"trial and error, and the results obtained."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:20
msgid "背景"
msgstr "background"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:22
msgid "以下のような構成でSphinxを使っていました："
msgstr "I was using Sphinx with the following configuration:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:24
msgid "多言語構成： ``ja``, ``en``"
msgstr "Multilingual configuration: ``ja``, ``en``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:25
msgid "``setup.py`` に ``doc`` コマンドを定義し、 ``python setup.py doc`` でビルド"
msgstr ""
"Define the ``doc`` command in ``setup.py`` and build with ``python setup.py "
"doc``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:26
msgid "poetry + poe を使って ``poetry run poe doc`` で実行"
msgstr "poetry + poe を使って ``poetry run poe doc`` で実行"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:27
msgid "最初のビルド時間： **約1分**"
msgstr "Initial build time: **about 1 minute**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:32
msgid "初期計測（改善前）"
msgstr "Initial measurement (before improvement)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:34
msgid "以下のように計測を行いました。"
msgstr "Measurements were made as follows."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:40
msgid "出力："
msgstr "output:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:46
msgid "この段階では、すべての言語を直列に、かつ ``-E -a`` オプション付きでフルビルドしていました。"
msgstr ""
"At this stage, all languages ​​were fully built serially and with the ``-E "
"-a`` option."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:51
msgid "改善施策の試行"
msgstr "Trial of improvement measures"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:53
msgid "次のような改善を順に試しました："
msgstr "I tried the following improvements in order:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:55
msgid "``-E -a`` の削除（差分ビルドを有効化）"
msgstr "Removed ``-E -a`` (enables differential builds)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:56
msgid "言語ごとの並列ビルド（``multiprocessing`` による）"
msgstr "Parallel builds per language (via ``multiprocessing``)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:57
msgid "静的ファイルコピーの差分対応（filecmpによる判定付き）"
msgstr "Difference support for static file copy (with judgment by filecmp)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:58
msgid "Sphinxの内部並列化（``-j auto`` オプション）"
msgstr "Sphinx internal parallelization (``-j auto`` option)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:59
msgid "コア数や仮想CPU環境による並列効果の検証"
msgstr ""
"Verification of parallelism effect by number of cores and virtual CPU "
"environment"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:64
msgid "Linuxでは、CPUのスペックは ``lscpu`` コマンドで確認できます。"
msgstr "On Linux, you can check the CPU specs with the ``lscpu`` command."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:69
msgid "最終構成（ベストプラクティス）"
msgstr "Final configuration (best practices)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:71
msgid "以下のような構成に落ち着きました："
msgstr "I ended up with a configuration like this:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:73
msgid "``-E -a`` を外し、差分ビルドを有効に"
msgstr "Remove ``-E -a`` and enable differential build"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:74
msgid "並列ビルドはあえて使わず、2コア環境では直列が安定"
msgstr ""
"I purposely do not use parallel build, and series is stable in a 2-core "
"environment."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:75
msgid "``-j auto`` を用いてSphinx内部の並列処理を有効に"
msgstr "Enable parallel processing inside Sphinx using ``-j auto``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:76
msgid "静的ファイルのコピーは差分判定付き"
msgstr "Static file copying includes difference judgment"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:81
msgid "改善後の計測結果"
msgstr "Measurement results after improvement"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:88
msgid "改善前と比較して **ビルド時間が6分の1以下に短縮** されました。"
msgstr ""
"**Build time has been reduced to less than 1/6th** compared to before the "
"improvement."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:93
msgid "考察と今後"
msgstr "Discussion and future"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:95
msgid "Sphinxはファイルキャッシュ（doctrees）を活用することで、大きく高速化可能"
msgstr "Sphinx can be greatly speeded up by using file cache (doctrees)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:96
msgid "CPUコア数が少ない環境では並列化の効果は限定的"
msgstr ""
"The effect of parallelization is limited in environments with a small number"
" of CPU cores."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:97
msgid "``-j auto`` による内部並列化は効果あり"
msgstr "Internal parallelization with ``-j auto`` is effective"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-27-sphinx-build-performance-optimization.rst:98
msgid "言語数が増えたり、仮想環境の構成が変わる場合は、再度並列処理の導入を検討"
msgstr ""
"If the number of languages ​​increases or the configuration of the virtual "
"environment changes, consider introducing parallel processing again."

